DataElement.preferredName: Biologically-Derived Material Product Material Lot Number Text ISO21090.ST.SIMPLE.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A substance made from living organisms or things they produce. EXAMPLE(S): virus, therapeutic serum, toxin, antitoxin, vaccine, blood, blood component or derivative, allergenic product, analogous product An alphanumeric string used to identify a particular batch of the product.
